  "detailed_description": "<strong>The brand new indie game hitting the screen, The curse of the ebony sword: Ebonside!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705620/extras/8b706a23e606a2853e7963ffe393a442.poster.avif?t=1705258918\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705620/extras/8b706a23e606a2853e7963ffe393a442.webm?t=1705258918\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705620/extras/8b706a23e606a2853e7963ffe393a442.mp4?t=1705258918\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>A Indie JRPG with a lot of features from crafting to dreaded boss fights!<br><br>As time pasts, the land that once housed life now houses a giant evil. And only you can stop it<br><br>Battle the darkness with classic classes from the old days of JRPGs with some new ones as well!<br>With a warrior, Black mage, Thief or a Dark Artisan, you can unlock and change into any class that<br>fits your playstyle!<br><br>Craft from hundreds of crafting trees! From carpentry, smiting, cooking and more!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705620/extras/8db7fc2ebf34d7a1a357abceeb8349ef.poster.avif?t=1705258918\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705620/extras/8db7fc2ebf34d7a1a357abceeb8349ef.webm?t=1705258918\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1705620/extras/8db7fc2ebf34d7a1a357abceeb8349ef.mp4?t=1705258918\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Breed and race your own kakata!<br><br>AND FIGHT BIG FRICKING MONSTERS!<br><br><strong>Key points!</strong><br>* Half decent story!<br>* Over 100 hours of Gameplay!<br>* Hundreds of Crafting recipes to learn and craft!<br>* Nine Classes to play and master!<br>* Rare monsters to find and hunt!<br>* A loveable cast of Characters!<br>*A Real time Day and Night system",
